  <dsc><c01 id="aspace_f0917c8859cab6c80489bf0b700dbe1a" level="series"><did><unittitle>Series I. Andrew Dickson White</unittitle></did><c02 id="aspace_bd1b1c30ac59bf2650377faf52b633c6" level="file"><did><unittitle>Andrew Dickson White inauguration</unittitle><unitdate datechar="creation" normal="1868-10-07/1921" type="inclusive">1868-10-07, 1921</unitdate><container id="aspace_19509a0c1a106c3fe8dd7a9c48c74d6d" label="Mixed Materials [31924113573749]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_6d89f2b0241046291a97e478bc5b92b2" parent="aspace_19509a0c1a106c3fe8dd7a9c48c74d6d" type="folder">1</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_72c848fdf8a5393a89b4c37b8456be78"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Includes two programs, two "reprints from the account of the proceedings at the Inauguration", and a photocopy of A.D. White's address</p></scopecontent></c02></c01><c01 id="aspace_5d9ee15b5e23d6867656298688de67c0" level="series"><did><unittitle>Series II. Charles Kendall Adams</unittitle></did><c02 id="aspace_12104a56887dd0be91d72495cc263c71" level="file"><did><unittitle>Charles Kendall Adams inauguration</unittitle><unitdate datechar="creation" normal="1885-11-19/1886" type="inclusive">1885-11-19-1886</unitdate><container id="aspace_077525493b47439791c6382c293cb0d4" label="Mixed Materials [31924113573749]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_90d972f7a495ef3d987d64f026166891" parent="aspace_077525493b47439791c6382c293cb0d4" type="folder">2</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_156d07c3dbfde467aa00cab966edc645"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Includes an invitation to the inauguration, a program, two copies of "Proceedings and Addresses as the Inauguration of Charles Kendall Adams", and a photocopy of the Cornell Era from November 20, 1885</p></scopecontent></c02></c01><c01 id="aspace_3d0a5c83456eafc000275d463c0cba2b" level="series"><did><unittitle>Series III. Jacob Gould Shurman</unittitle></did><c02 id="aspace_89c31498f827b42fe1402cf7e64308c7" level="file"><did><unittitle>Jacob Gould Schurman inauguration</unittitle><unitdate datechar="creation" normal="1892-11-11/1892-11-11" type="inclusive">1892-11-11</unitdate><container id="aspace_d87dae8a0d303e2803a245c29703c104" label="Mixed Materials [31924113573749]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_1f0bfb40bcece0a351d6bcdb105e099f" parent="aspace_d87dae8a0d303e2803a245c29703c104" type="folder">3</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_bdc8d904f7d3c13908f83524562d21a2"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Includes copy of "Inauguration of President Schurman" and photocopied excerpt of book</p></scopecontent></c02></c01><c01 id="aspace_3b87c06d28e404151c83bdf8d603b97d" level="series"><did><unittitle>Series IV. Livingston Farrand</unittitle></did><c02 id="aspace_113e4e109ea9241ab1017ccf6bce8b79" level="file"><did><unittitle>Livingston Farrand inauguration</unittitle><unitdate datechar="creation" normal="1921-06-30/1921-10-20" type="inclusive">1921-06-30-1921-10-20</unitdate><container id="aspace_616da6fd71e9cb352b8ae46626748c15" label="Mixed Materials [31924113573749]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_aa3a267daac960da895e4bd85d62d902" parent="aspace_616da6fd71e9cb352b8ae46626748c15" type="folder">4</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_3d6d531d524aa49468ce0277800f137d"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Includes two programs, program for inaugural dinner, information pamphlet for those participating in ceremony, in a copy of "Inauguration of Livingston Farrand Fourth President of Cornell University" and photocopied excerpt of book and Alumni news</p></scopecontent></c02></c01><c01 id="aspace_2dc4c895e046ceb49eee4aa20d5ffcc4" level="series"><did><unittitle>Series V. Edmund Ezra Day</unittitle></did><c02 id="aspace_70b85522f42ee1d983b109ed69843712" level="file"><did><unittitle>Edmund Ezra Day inauguration</unittitle><unitdate datechar="creation" normal="1936-11-12/1937-10-08" type="inclusive">1936-11-12-1937-10-08</unitdate><container id="aspace_7