for inaugural lunch, two copies of "Inauguration of James Alfred Perkins", and information regarding the University Mace and Baton - first used in Perkins inauguration</p></scopecontent></c02></c01><c01 id="aspace_e9f1fd588223d459a798110d21fee6eb" level="series"><did><unittitle>Series VIII. Dale R. Corson</unittitle></did><c02 id="aspace_1dfbfd87979c33e983a602bfc15e5214" level="file"><did><unittitle>Dale R. Corson inauguration</unittitle><unitdate datechar="creation" normal="1969-10/1976-06" type="inclusive">1969-10-1970-06-08, 1976-06</unitdate><container id="aspace_fd9010e1e616f809f92c1469a9a1cfaf" label="Mixed Materials [31924113573749]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_dd6ad49ea3834ff22916b2f37de1c472" parent="aspace_fd9010e1e616f809f92c1469a9a1cfaf" type="folder">8</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_a238edcdcac2abb8db72bee974c90f26"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Includes program for inaugural dinner, information about guests and menu for dinner, Commencement and Investiture of the President program, note from Corson's office explaining why his inauguration took place when it did, inaugural address, photocopied pages from Ithaca Journal, and photocopied article from Alumni news</p></scopecontent></c02></c01><c01 id="aspace_f34ec4f6fa5cd1f694d3a2631082973a" level="series"><did><unittitle>Series IX. Frank H. T. Rhodes</unittitle></did><c02 id="aspace_e62facdfd68c95e85a044340006db5e2" level="file"><did><unittitle>Frank H. T. Rhodes inauguration</unittitle><unitdate datechar="creation" normal="1977-11-10/1977-11-10" type="inclusive">1977-11-10</unitdate><container id="aspace_d2d31ca8c14f47a798c526d509ce692d" label="Mixed Materials [31924113573749]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_4ffcb539dc6a93e5f278e8e90894f415" parent="aspace_d2d31ca8c14f47a798c526d509ce692d" type="folder">9</container></did></c02></c01><c01 id="aspace_cd6f5d5dd5b7d8737cc7ef92ed8d0ff1" level="series"><did><unittitle>Series X. Hunter R. Rawlings III</unittitle>